title: I will regret it my whole life
review: I want my money back!Not just for tickets, but for F popcorn as well and Fanta too as that guy ran out of Coke. What is wrong with you? I really can't believe anyone who is able to watch this more than 10-20 minutes. Those guys can't be my friends. What a scam! Really??? Only reason I was watching it is because I had juice and popcorn and it was shame to leave it.
